# Cross-origin isolation → enables SharedArrayBuffer → multi-threaded wasm for
# onnxruntime-web (the Khmer voice) and transformers.js (the LLM), which is
# several times faster than single-thread. `credentialless` COEP keeps
# same-origin/cross-origin resource loading working without needing CORP on
# every asset (safer than require-corp). Served by Cloudflare Workers assets.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: credentialless
